Package org.anchoranalysis.plugin.quick.bean.input

Class QuickBase<T extends InputFromManager>

Object
AnchorBean<InputManager<T>>
InputManager<T>
QuickBase<T>
Type Parameters:
T - input-type
Direct Known Subclasses:
MultiInputManagerQuick, NamedChannelsQuick
public abstract class QuickBase<T extends InputFromManager>
extends InputManager<T>
A base for quick managers that make various assumptions about file-structure.

This provides a quicker means to specify certain projects.

Author:
Owen Feehan

    • getRegex

      public String getRegex()
      A regular-expression applied to the image file-path that matches three groups. The first group should correspond to the unique name of the top-level owner The second group should correspond to the unique name of the dataset. The third group should correspond to the unique name of the experiment.
